public abstract class ProlAbstractCatcheableException
extends ProlException

The class describes a Prol Exception which can be catched with the catch/3 predicate and it can be throws with the throw/1 predicate. It's an abstract class so it can't have any direct instance.

Author:
Igor Maznitsa (igor.maznitsa@igormaznitsa.com)
